1
00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:00,934
Actually,

2
00:00:00,935 --> 00:00:02,601
we've reviewed both your profiles.

3
00:00:02,602 --> 00:00:04,069
Since you both meet the requirements,

4
00:00:04,070 --> 00:00:05,605
we wanted to bring you in for a chat.

5
00:00:05,905 --> 00:00:07,606
It wasn't supposed to be this complicated,

6
00:00:07,607 --> 00:00:09,376
but the director wanted
to see more options.

7
00:00:09,609 --> 00:00:10,609
Which is fine.

8
00:00:10,944 --> 00:00:12,745
We need to find the perfect fit,

9
00:00:12,746 --> 00:00:13,480
don't we?

10
00:00:13,481 --> 00:00:15,548
I'm not about to ruin my reputation.

11
00:00:17,384 --> 00:00:18,084
Director,

12
00:00:18,085 --> 00:00:20,286
how would you like to test them?

13
00:00:22,589 --> 00:00:23,889
You two,

14
00:00:23,890 --> 00:00:25,325
do a chemistry read with Shasha.

15
00:00:29,763 --> 00:00:30,763
What's Hei Yan's problem?

16
00:00:31,030 --> 00:00:32,550
It's already rigged, why the audition?

17
00:00:32,932 --> 00:00:34,692
I heard the director
is a handful this time.

18
00:00:34,834 --> 00:00:36,468
He probably just wants to avoid any gossip.

19
00:00:36,469 --> 00:00:37,404
Give me a break.

20
00:00:37,405 --> 00:00:38,704
If he weren't such a good actor,

21
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:39,705
I wouldn't even bother.

22
00:00:56,256 --> 00:00:57,456
Aren't we doing a screen test?

23
00:00:58,291 --> 00:00:59,291
Let's get started.

24
00:01:00,827 --> 00:01:02,195
You don't even know the prompt.

25
00:01:02,595 --> 00:01:03,863
You're just going to wing it?

26
00:01:04,964 --> 00:01:05,765
It's just a formality.

27
00:01:05,766 --> 00:01:06,865
Why make a scene?

28
00:01:06,866 --> 00:01:08,168
I am your senior, after all.

29
00:01:10,203 --> 00:01:11,504
Since you're the senior,

30
00:01:12,105 --> 00:01:14,073
you should be setting an example.

31
00:01:14,908 --> 00:01:15,908
Alright.

32
00:01:16,743 --> 00:01:19,678
In a moment, improvise a confession scene.

33
00:01:19,679 --> 00:01:21,147
I'll give you ten minutes.

34
00:01:26,753 --> 00:01:27,920
Hi, Shasha.

35
00:01:27,921 --> 00:01:28,755
I'm Bai Xing.

36
00:01:28,756 --> 00:01:30,256
It's an honor to meet you.

37
00:01:41,468 --> 00:01:42,469
Action.

38
00:01:43,937 --> 00:01:45,038
So, will you be with me?

39
00:01:48,708 --> 00:01:49,976
Why should I say yes?

40
00:01:52,345 --> 00:01:53,345
Why wouldn't you?

41
00:01:54,747 --> 00:01:55,782
Give me one reason.

42
00:01:58,651 --> 00:02:00,091
Is it because you don't feel I'm worthy,

43
00:02:01,087 --> 00:02:02,422
or because it's not worth it?

44
00:02:08,394 --> 00:02:10,229
Okay, let's cut it there.

45
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:11,296
That was great, thank you.

46
00:02:11,297 --> 00:02:13,465
Thanks, Shasha and Hei Yan.

47
00:02:13,466 --> 00:02:14,734
Bai Xing, you're up next.
